      • sameId

        public static <T> T sameId(@Nonnull
                           T other)
        Argument matcher that uses reflection to invoke the getId() method. Important: this method is used ONLY in Mockito verify() methods and is defined to return null. The method is however not annotated Nullable to avoid all sorts of nullability warnings which are not relevant for those verify() methods.
        Type Parameters:
        T - Class.
        Parameters:
        other - The object to match the argument with.
        Returns:
        Always null.
